Too many cows.

362
00:35:06,370 --> 00:35:08,606
Well, fortunately this isn't
   about cows.

363
00:35:08,639 --> 00:35:09,874
And it's not about
what you want, either.

364
00:35:09,907 --> 00:35:13,578
It's not about your loyalty
to the company
or the common good.

365
00:35:13,611 --> 00:35:17,181
And it's definitely not about
  saving the world for
  democracy, no.

366
00:35:18,249 --> 00:35:21,452
It's about you owe me, Della.

367
00:35:22,954 --> 00:35:25,590
It's about paying debts.

368
00:35:25,623 --> 00:35:27,792
It's about staying
out of prison.

369
00:35:27,825 --> 00:35:31,829
It has to do with you
protecting what's left
of your family.

370
00:35:33,464 --> 00:35:35,199
You have no choice.

371
00:35:38,369 --> 00:35:41,772
Maybe not, Neil,
   at least for the moment,

372
00:35:41,806 --> 00:35:46,944
but if anything goes wrong,
anything at all,

373
00:35:46,978 --> 00:35:50,448
you and I are gonna share
   one last dance together.

374
00:35:50,481 --> 00:35:54,485
There's a particularly zealous
 militia operating out
 of a company

375
