376
00:35:57,889 --> 00:36:01,492
It's run by a clown
  named Arno Taylor.

377
00:36:01,526 --> 00:36:04,762
He fancies himself as one of
   the original Green Mountain
   boys. (CHUCKLES WRYLY)

378
00:36:04,795 --> 00:36:08,633
Indications are that they're
   stock-piling weapons
   and explosives,

379
00:36:08,666 --> 00:36:11,369
and it seems they have more
   than a political agenda.

380
00:36:11,402 --> 00:36:12,637
They have a plan.

381
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:14,572
And it's dangerous.

382
00:36:14,605 --> 00:36:15,873
And we wanna know what it is.

383
00:36:17,675 --> 00:36:19,744
There's a vehicle downstairs,
  keys are in it.

384
00:36:19,777 --> 00:36:21,546
Everything
 else is in the file.

385
00:36:21,579 --> 00:36:23,648
Contacts, locations,
 support, everything
 you need and, Della?

386
00:36:25,816 --> 00:36:27,485
No one's looking for you now.

