MAN: Look out, there's
 purse-snatchers
 over there.

441
00:40:59,690 --> 00:41:02,092
So, let me see if I understand
 this, officer.

442
00:41:02,126 --> 00:41:03,194
You're letting
   them go?

443
00:41:05,296 --> 00:41:07,531
Well, I admit, the odds
 didn't look so good,

444
00:41:07,565 --> 00:41:09,600
but the results
 weren't what I was expecting.

445
00:41:09,633 --> 00:41:11,969
Seems to me they sustained
 most of the damage.

446
00:41:12,002 --> 00:41:14,605
Those boys are bad news.

447
00:41:14,638 --> 00:41:16,140
Why'd you mix it up with them
  in the first place?

448
00:41:18,242 --> 00:41:19,777
Just for the taste of it.

449
00:41:19,810 --> 00:41:20,878
