  you've been warned.

480
00:42:49,433 --> 00:42:51,802
-Now you stay out of trouble.
  -I will.

481
00:42:54,972 --> 00:42:57,875
-And by the way...
  -(CAR DOOR CLOSES)

482
00:42:57,908 --> 00:43:00,244
