  intimate terms with young
   Jethro's nose.

485
00:43:07,217 --> 00:43:08,852
Thanks.

486
00:43:08,886 --> 00:43:11,989
Uh, one more thing.
Where are you staying?

487
00:43:12,022 --> 00:43:13,757
I don't know yet.

488
00:43:13,791 --> 00:43:16,427
-That's right,
 you just arrived.
 -Yes.

489
00:43:16,460 --> 00:43:18,295
Employment?

490
00:43:18,329 --> 00:43:20,164
Like I said,
 that's why I'm here.

