01:30:07,902 --> 01:30:09,737
(SIRENS WAILING DISTANTLY)

976
01:30:41,569 --> 01:30:43,838
(AIRPLANE WHOOSHING)

977
01:31:16,704 --> 01:31:19,540
That was a major setback.

978
01:31:19,574 --> 01:31:21,175
-How long to JFK?
  -(SIGHS) Oh, I don't know.

979
01:31:22,210 --> 01:31:23,978
Pilot, what's our ETA?

980
01:31:24,011 --> 01:31:25,146
Gentlemen.

981
01:31:25,847 --> 01:31:27,715
Della.

982
01:31:27,748 --> 01:31:29,617
You look surprised, Neil.

983
01:31:29,650 --> 01:31:30,985
What do you want, Dellacourt?

984
01:31:31,018 --> 01:31:32,987
He wants his revenge, Taylor.

985
01:31:33,020 --> 01:31:35,289
No, nothing so crude
  as revenge.

986
01:31:35,323 --> 01:31:37,625
No? What then?

987
01:31:37,658 --> 01:31:40,995
I want retribution.
   You stole my life, Neil.

988
01:31:41,028 --> 01:31:43,030
Oh, come on, Della.

989
01:31:43,064 --> 01:31:45,933
We can work together
  and make things better,
  like we always do.

990
01:31:45,967 --> 01:31:51,072
I don't think we ever made
 anything better.
 Maybe just different.

991
01:31:51,105 --> 01:31:55,142
You're a talented man,
   Mr. Dellacourt.
   Take his advice.

992
01:31:55,176 --> 01:31:57,778
No thank you, Mr. Taylor.

993
01:31:57,812 --> 01:32:01,582
But for old times' sake, Neil,
 I'll leave you with some
 advice of my own.

994
01:32:04,285 --> 01:32:05,920
Make a last wish.

995
01:32:17,164 --> 01:32:18,833
(MOUTHING)

996
01:32:57,805 --> 01:32:58,906
Hi, there.
   Where you going?

997
01:32:58,940 --> 01:33:00,374
Wilmington, Delaware.

998
01:33:00,408 --> 01:33:02,410
What in the world is in
 Wilmington, Delaware?

999
01:33:02,443 --> 01:33:04,211
You know,
 I don't know anymore.

1000
01:33:04,245 --> 01:33:06,948
Pile in. I don't wanna
 keep a man from
 his destiny. Pile in.

1001
01:33:09,951 --> 01:33:13,387
(MELLOW TUNE PLAYING ON PIANO)

1002
01:34:02,036 --> 01:34:05,406
(INSTRUMENTAL MUSIC PLAYING)

